title: Combine takeaways & awards
itunes:title: Combine takeaways & awards
description:
A Lucas Oil Stadium filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Kevin Patra and Conor Orr -- break down all the latest from the 2015 NFL Scouting Combine plus updates on Peyton Manning, Adrian Peterson and much more. The guys then wrap the show with the first ever (and probably only) Combine Coaches and GM Pressers Awards.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
